title: The Weepies - Say I Am You (2006)
description:
------------------------------------
The second album from The Weepies.

Very hard to categorize and define a genre...
Indie? Folk? Twee? Singer/Songwriter? Pop? Emo? All of the mentioned? 
Anyway, beautiful harmonies, beautiful voices.
